There is something going on. Many feel it but they don't know what it is. What is coming is the most perilous time the Planet has ever seen. It has many names. The End Times, The 70th Week of Daniel or The Times of Jacobs Trouble, it doesn't matter which one you choose to call it. They all have the same outcome. 7 years after the Rapture, Jesus returns to kick butt on the dEVIL that is all around us.

A few of us will attending The Marriage Supper of The Lamb. It is the Wedding Party for Jesus and His Church. The Church is the Bride of Christ. The Bible Promises us we will not go through the COMING ARMAGEDDON. THE FOUR HORSEMAN OF THE Apocalypse WILL BE RIDING SOON.

DON'T BE HERE WHEN THEY COME. Here is how to avoid these times.
